    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>As a bonus action, you issue a challenge that compels other creatures to do battle with you. Each creature of your choice that you can see within 30 feet of you must make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, a creature can't willingly move more than 30 feet away from you. This effect ends on the creature if you are &amp;Reference[condition=incapacitated] or die or if the creature is more than 30 feet away from you.</p></div>",
